Hey there! It looks like the ability to add ad credit isn't available for newly created accounts by default. To become eligible, your account must complete and pass business verification, and accumulate over $5,000 in spend. Once these conditions are met, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
